ck-nointro
==========

Skip intro mod for Core Keeper.

Note
====

To make symlinks work, you need to use Proton. This stops Core Keeper to using

	$HOME/.config/unity3d/Pugstorm/Core\ Keeper

and instead uses

	.anchor/compatdata/1621690/pfx/
	drive_c/users/steamuser/AppData/LocalLow/Pugstorm/Core\ Keeper
